title: Trillian Astra 6.0 Build 61 + Patch
description:
[b]Description:[/b]
Trillian Astra Pro 6.0 Build 61   
Recently, a well-known instant messenger program for the Windows operating system has been updated, and you can also download versions for Apple, Mac OS X, Android and other devices, for this you need to visit the official website of the project. Plus the client can safely be called multiprotokolnost, in addition to ICQ you will be able to communicate in AIM, IRC, JAbber, Skype and so on, try to download Trillian, you may like it, especially built-in Russian support, which has not existed for a long time.
I also want to note the plus of the client, you can simultaneously connect to several protocols and exchange messages, but you will not need to run several development projects, and all your contacts will be in a single window, which will be divided in such a way that you immediately understand Which protocol the contact belongs to. Trillian has a pretty attractive interface, I would call it stylish, the color scheme can be changed, and you can also add various plug-ins.
various plug-ins.
